'''''Pumzi''''' ni film ngufi ya siyanse y'impimbano yo muri Kenya yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Wanuri Kahiu<ref>https://www.e-flux.com/video/334045/wanuri-kahiu-nbsp-pumzi/</ref> . Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2010 mu rwego rwa gahunda yayo nshya ya Afurika<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/pumzi/</ref>.    Uyu mushinga watewe inkunga  n’ikigega cy’ubuhanzi cya Changamoto, ndetse n’ikigo cya Goethe Institut na Focus Features <ref>https://www.wired.com/2010/01/pumzi/</ref>. Kahiu yizeye kwagura bigufi muburyo bwuzuye<ref>https://africa.film/pumzi-a-wanuri-kahiu-short-film/</ref>.  Filime iri mucyongereza,  ariko umutwe ni [[Igiswahili]] bisobanuye"Umwuka<ref>https://www.theafricareport.com/8939/films-pumzi-and-scheherazade-tell-me-a-story/</ref>". 

=== Afurika ===
Pumzi igwa cyane mubwoko bwa Africanfuturism <ref>https://uniteyouthdublin.wordpress.com/2015/08/31/pumzi-a-review/</ref>. Irerekana uko ejo hazaza hazaba umuco (uherereye kumugabane wa Afrika) utuwe cyane nabirabura<ref>https://www.pumzithefilm.com/</ref>. Byongeye kandi, yakozwe na sitidiyo yo muri Afrika yepfo igizwe nitsinda ryabashinzwe gukora no kumenyekanisha uburyo bushya bwibintu ndangamuco biva mubihugu bya Afrika<ref>https://www.international.ucla.edu/ccs/event/9186</ref>. ''Pumzi'' ihuza neza na motif ikunze kuboneka muri Africanfuturism , ariko ntibigarukiraho gusa, kuba hari ahantu nyaburanga hatagira uruhare runini rw'amazi<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/movie/144513/pumzi</ref>.

